            <h3 class="ttl"><span class="ttl-accent">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_sec_title')}</span></h3>
            <p class="sub">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_sec_sub')}</p>
            <div class="more">
              Credentials live locally at <code class="mono">~/.capgo-credentials/credentials.json</code>, are sent only to ephemeral build envs over HTTPS, and are wiped the
              instant the build ends. Logs stream to your terminal and are never written to Capgo disk.
            </div>
