                ><path d="M12 16V5"></path><path d="M8 9l4-4 4 4"></path><path d="M5 19h14"></path></svg
              ></span
            >
            <h3 class="ttl"><span class="ttl-accent">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_asc_title')}</span></h3>
            <p class="sub">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_asc_sub')}</p>
            <div class="more">
              Default <code class="mono">app_store</code> distribution uploads straight to App Store Connect / TestFlight via Fastlane; Android bundles go to the Play Console. Pick
              <code class="mono">ad_hoc</code> for internal-only iOS builds. Skips ASC validation.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tile" data-expandable data-accent="orange">
            <span class="icon"
              ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"
                ><path d="M3 12h3l2.5-7 5 14 2.5-7H21"></path></svg
              ></span
            >
            <h3 class="ttl"><span class="ttl-accent">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_logs_title')}</span></h3>
            <p class="sub">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_logs_sub')}</p>
            <div class="more">
              Logs stream over WebSocket with heartbeat + ack. A <code class="mono">qr_download_link</code> message renders a scannable QR + URL for APK / IPA downloads right in your
              terminal.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tile" data-expandable data-accent="pink">
            <span class="icon"
              ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"
                ><path d="M12 3l9 5-9 5-9-5z"></path><path d="M3 13l9 5 9-5"></path></svg
              ></span
            >
            <h3 class="ttl"><span class="ttl-accent">{copy('native_build_v2_tile_flavors_title')}</span></h3>
